CNCP v1 28244
{
  "concept": "vuejs/core#5933: Extraneous non-props attributes (class) were passed to component but could not be automatically inherited because component renders fragment or text root nodes.",
  "version": "1.0",
  "created_at": "2026-03-15T04:26:16.717298+00:00",
  "text": "Extraneous non-props attributes (class) were passed to component but could not be automatically inherited because component renders fragment or text root nodes.\n\n### Link to minimal reproduction\r\n\r\nhttps://sfc.vuejs.org/#\r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\nCreate a component with conditional rendering, **each condition already has a single root.**\r\n\r\n```vue\r\n<template>\r\n  <template v-if=\"to\">\r\n    <RouterLink v-if=\"isRoute\" :to=\"href\" v-bind=\"commonAttrs\" :class=\"classList\">\r\n      <slot />\r\n    </RouterLink>\r\n    <a v-else :href=\"href\" v-bind=\"commonAttrs\" :class=\"classList\">\r\n      <slot />\r\n    </a>\r\n  </template>\r\n  <div v-else v-bind=\"commonAttrs\" :class=\"classList\">\r\n    <slot />\r\n  </div>\r\n</template>\r\n<script lang=\"ts\" setup>\r\nimport { computed, inject, useAttrs } from 'vue'\r\nimport type { RouteLocationRaw } from 'vue-router'\r\nimport useLink from './useLink.ts'\r\n\r\ninterface Props {\r\n  to?: RouteLocationRaw\r\n}\r\n\r\nconst props = defineProps<Props>()\r\nconst emit = defineEmits(['click'])\r\n\r\nconst attrs = useAttrs()\r\nconst { href, isRoute } = useLink(props, attrs)\r\n\r\nconst classList = computed(() => {\r\n  return ['e-menu-item']\r\n})\r\n\r\nconst onClick = () => {\r\n  console.log('click')\r\n}\r\n\r\nconst onMouseover = () => {\r\n  console.log('mouseover')\r\n}\r\n\r\nconst commonAttrs = {\r\n  ...attrs,\r\n  onClick,\r\n  onMouseover,\r\n}\r\n</script>\r\n```\r\n\r\nwhen I use this component and pass a class attribute it outputs the following warning.\r\n\r\n```vue\r\n<MenuItem class=\"menu-item\" to=\"/user/settings\">\r\n  Profile\r\n</MenuItem>\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n`[Vue warn]: Extraneous non-props attributes (class) were passed to component but could not be automatically inherited because component renders fragment or text root nodes.`\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1202\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/59635374/168699398-d5fca831-f48c-48ac-96d8-fd050f192004.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n### What is expected?\r\n\r\nShould not show this warning as the component is rendering with a single root.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### What is actually happening?\r\n\r\nThis is the rendered HTML with the warning `[Vue warn]: Extraneous non-props attributes (class) were passed to component but could not be automatically inherited because component renders fragment or text root nodes.`\r\n```\r\n<a href=\"/user/settings\" class=\"menu-item e-menu-item\"><!--[--> Profile <!--]--></a>\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n### System Info\r\n\r\n```shell\r\nSystem:\r\n    OS: macOS 10.15.7\r\n    CPU: (12) x64 Intel(R) Core(TM) i7-9750H CPU @ 2.60GHz\r\n    Memory: 934.50 MB / 16.00 GB\r\n    Shell: 5.7.1 - /bin/zsh\r\n  Binaries:\r\n    Node: 16.8.0 - /usr/local/bin/node\r\n    Yarn: 1.22.17 - ~/.yarn/bin/yarn\r\n    npm: 7.21.0 - /usr/local/bin/npm\r\n  Browsers:\r\n    Chrome: 101.0.4951.64\r\n    Edge: 101.0.1210.47\r\n    Firefox: 100.0\r\n    Safari: 15.4\r\n```\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n### Any additional comments?\r\n\r\n_No response_",
  "language": "en",
  "keywords": [
    "scope: compiler",
    "🔩 p2-edge-case"
  ],
